    • Method Detail

      • getByName

        ResourceCollection<T> getByName(String name)
        Retrieves a paginated collection (ResourceCollection) containing the details for the available resources found under the current HPE OneView that match the name provided.

        The filter applied in this case is as follows: 

             filter="name matches 'name'"
        Parameters:
        name - name that should be used to filter the resources found in HPE OneView.
        Returns:
        ResourceCollection paginated collection containing the details for the available resources if type <T> that match the filter.
